Face Detection Accuracy

This project is a Face Detection Comparison Tool that evaluates the performance of different AI models for detecting faces in images.

The application allows the user to:
•	Load a folder containing images
•	Manually draw Ground Truth bounding boxes for faces
•	Run different AI face detection models
•	Compare their performance using Precision, Recall, and F1 Score

AI Models Used
The project compares three face detection models:
•	MTCNN
•	MediaPipe Face Detection
•	Faster R-CNN

Application Features
Simple GUI interface using Tkinter
Manual drawing of ground truth face boxes
Detection using multiple AI models
Performance evaluation metrics:
•	Precision
•	Recall
•	F1 Score
Image navigation (Next / Previous)

